      particlesim.DrawParticles
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable, java.util.concurrent.Future<java.lang.Void>, java.util.EventListener, javax.media.opengl.GLEventListener
public class DrawParticles
extends org.jdesktop.swingworker.SwingWorker<java.lang.Void,java.awt.Graphics>
implements javax.media.opengl.GLEventListener

This class handles drawing an array of IParticle onto the GL panel. It extends the SwingWorker class in order to do all of the work in a seperate thread; this prevent the interface from locking up.
